OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FLow cloud
OL,6,Falong the coast will spread inland
OL,7,Fthis evening driven by a moderate
OL,8,Fbreeze off the North Sea. Some fog
OL,9,Fpatches and spots of drizzle are
OL,10,Fpossible. Staying mild overnight.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSunday:FPerhaps rather cloudy to
OL,13,Fstart, soon clearing to give lengthy
OL,14,Fsunny spells. Cloud may linger near
OL,15,Fcoasts. Warm or very warm inland,
OL,16,Fcooler near coasts especially in the
OL,17,Fbreeze.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
