OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:
OL,6,FLargely dry through this period, with
OL,7,Fcloud developing overnight, burning
OL,8,Fback to coasts by day to give sunny
OL,9,Fspells. Perhaps an isolated thundery
OL,10,Fshower on Wednesday. Warm or very warm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
